  <brief_title>A Clinical Study for Assessment of the Efficacy and Safety of Mirtazapine (Smilon) in Depression Patients With Pain</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase IV Study for Evaluation the Efficacy and Safety of Mirtazapine (Smilon) in Depression Patients With Pain</official_title>
