  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Smilon® in the Depression
      Patients with pain. Eligible patients will be randomly assigned to 1 of 2 arms, either
      Smilon® or placebo, and will receive the treatment for 8 weeks in this study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
